    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can you precise how it would look like in term of html `<scripts>`? (an example of `<scripts>` tags).\n\nWhat do you think the usecase is here? Something like a user already having `<script src=react/lodash` etc.. Wanting to share his `<script>` dependencies with us?\n\nIf so we can make all big dependencies externals in a specific build but I am unsure of the usage.\n\nI expect people in need of optimization to already use things like npm and not relying on script tags to include react/lodash..?\n\nDo you need it somehow in shopify?\n",
