    "body": "We are not going to do it right away. For our usage, we are going to do bundles everytime.\n\nAfter talking with @Jerskouille, this came up:\nThe use case \"a `<script>` user is aware enough to be wanting to optimize the usage of his own `<script>` tags by sharing dependencies without using browserify/webpack AND he found the relevant documentation in our website\" should be very rare or non-existent.\n\nIf I am wrong here I am happy to provide :beers: to both @Jerskouille and our user if that happen.\n",
