  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I have the same issue. Just moved to the cdn of instantsearch.js from webpack. You seem to be having lodash 2 times, one in algoliasearch and in instantsearch.js and we're loading lodash the 3rd time in our own project, but we're only loading what we need with webpack you seem to be loading everything. \n\nEven the CDN version is 400k minified.. (//cdn.jsdelivr.net/instantsearch.js/1/instantsearch.min.js)\n",
